msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_001"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A <2.se_co>treasure hidden inside a sandstorm by\n"
"an ancient civilization<3.re_co>...\n"
"The makings of a fine adventure for sure.\n"
"<4.so>They say the sandstorm lets up for a few\n"
"hours each day, but I haven't seen it\n"
"settle down for even an instant.\n"
"I've had my eyes glued to it all this time.<5.pa>\n"
"Except for when I've fallen asleep..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: sound
#. 3: text_size
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_002"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so>Tomorrow will be the day I see this sandstorm swirl\n"
"to a halt... I just know it!<3.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_003"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Shifty merchants? Sorry, no idea\n"
"what you're talking about.\n"
"\n"
"The only things I'm interested in right\n"
"now are this sandstorm and the treasure\n"
"hiding inside its...<2.pa>storming...<3.pa>sands..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_004"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A <2.se_co>treasure hidden inside a sandstorm by\n"
"an ancient civilization<3.re_co>...\n"
"\n"
"Sounds like an adventure just waiting\n"
"to happen.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>They say the sandstorm lets up for a few\n"
"hours each day, but I haven't seen it\n"
"settle down for even an instant.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_005"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I haven't taken my eyes off this\n"
"sandstorm for days. Except for when\n"
"I've fallen asleep..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_006"
msgid ""
"<1.so>And that brings me to my next point!<2.pa>\n"
"...Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_007"
msgid ""
"OK, OK, I know I keep asking you this,\n"
"but...<1.pa> Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_008"
msgid "<1.so>Wait, who did you say you are again?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_010"
msgid ""
"<1.so>An adventure like this has been a lifelong\n"
"dream! You could never understand!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_011"
msgid "<1.so>Not now! You'll distract me!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (long)
#. 6: pause (short)
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_F_012"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh?<2.pa> Did it...<3.pa>\n"
"Did the sandstorm stop?!\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>After all this time watching it...<5.pa>\n"
"Why did it just disappear like that?<6.pa>\n"
"What a mystery!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_R_001"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That sandstorm... They say it stops for\n"
"a few hours a day, but it hasn't let up\n"
"even a little since I've been watching."
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: sound
#. 3: text_size
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_R_002"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so>Tomorrow will be the day I see this sandstorm swirl\n"
"to a halt... I just know it!<3.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (longer)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "Npc_SmallOasis007_R_005"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Rumor has it <2.se_co>an ancient civilization hid a\n"
"treasure<3.re_co> inside that sandstorm.\n"
"\n"
"I've been here for days waiting for the\n"
"storm to settle down so I can nab it!<4.pa>\n"
"<5.so>I just hope it wasn't a bad lead..."
msgstr ""

